<p>NobodyWho Chat collects no personal data. All AI processing happens on your device. Nothing you say or type ever
    leaves your device. We have no servers, no accounts, and no analytics. The only information that ever leaves your device
    is anonymous crash diagnostics, described in detail below.</p>
<h2>1. Who we are</h2>
<p>NobodyWho Chat is developed and distributed by NobodyWho. NobodyWho is an inference engine that lets you run LLMs
    locally and efficiently on any device.</p>
<p>This Privacy Policy applies solely to the NobodyWho Chat application available on the Apple App Store (iOS) and the
    Google Play Store (Android). It does not apply to any other products or services we may offer.</p>
<h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
